metadata.title: US NMFS - Commercial Fisheries Statistics
metadata.description:
Measurement Details
Landings or commercial species (by year, by state, by species, by gear type. Available annually 1950-1996 and month 1990-1996.

Geographic Area
Atlantic, Gulf of Mexico and Pacific Oceans

Data Distribution
database reach and data retrieval available at this web site

Base Internet/URL ( http://www.st.nmfs.gov/st1/index.html )

[ A TCODE project ]
